---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portland Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in Portland, Maine. Local regulations, best locations, and market opportunities.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Portland Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Portland, Maine</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Portland, Maine's largest city, offers the state's most robust cannabis market. With a population of 68,000+ and millions of annual tourists, Portland presents significant opportunities for dispensary operators—along with notable competition.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Portland Market</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>68,000+ (130k+ metro)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Tourism</td><td>High - summer & fall seasons</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Moderate-High</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>Premium ($25-40/sq ft)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Regulations</td><td>Portland has local ordinances</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local Regulations</h2>
      <p>Portland has specific local regulations for cannabis businesses:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Local license required in addition to state license</li>
        <li>Zoning restrictions apply</li>
        <li>Distance requirements from schools (300+ feet)</li>
        <li>Operating hours may be restricted</li>
        <li>Signage regulations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations in Portland</h2>
      
      <h3>Recommended Areas:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Congress Street</strong> - High foot traffic, commercial district</li>
        <li><strong>Forest Avenue</strong> - Retail corridor, good visibility</li>
        <li><strong>Commercial Street</strong> - Old Port area, tourist traffic</li>
        <li><strong>Outer Congress</strong> - More affordable, still accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Areas to Avoid:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Near schools and playgrounds</li>
        <li>Residential neighborhoods (check zoning)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Competition</h2>
      <p>Portland has several established dispensaries. To compete:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Differentiate through product selection</li>
        <li>Focus on customer experience</li>
        <li>Strong local branding</li>
        <li>Premium positioning vs. budget options</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Investment Requirements</h2>
      <p>Portland premium real estate means higher startup costs:</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Estimated Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Real Estate (lease)</td><td>$5,000-10,000/mo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Build-out</td><td>$150,000-350,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total Investment</td><td>$500,000-1.2M</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Success Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Build relationships with local cultivators</li>
        <li>Leverage tourism with unique products</li>
        <li>Invest in customer education</li>
        <li>Strong social media presence</li>
        <li>Consider delivery services</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Research Portland-specific ordinances</li>
        <li>Consult with local cannabis attorney</li>
        <li>Identify specific locations</li>
        <li>Apply for local license</li>
        <li>Apply for state license</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>This is for informational purposes only. Verify all requirements with Portland officials and Maine OCP.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul, ol { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
